title: Policy6145(A)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Interscholastic athletics comprise an integral part of the educational program for Regional School District 8. Athletics enrich the educational program by providing an experience that fosters physical, social, and emotional growth of students through comprehensive teaching practices and appropriately competitive experiences. Our athletics program should promote high standards of academic achievement, good citizenship and individual responsibility on the playing field, in the school and in the community. In so doing, the athletics program complements and supports the academic program.
